<h2 style="margin:0 0 16px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;">Confirm your email</h2>

<p style="font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#374151;line-height:1.5;">
  Welcome to Ike<%= ", #{@user.name}" if @user.name.present? %>! Confirm <strong><%= @user.email %></strong> to activate your account. This link expires in 24 hours and works once.
</p>

<p style="margin:24px 0;">
  <%= link_to "Confirm my email", @confirm_url, style: "display:inline-block;padding:10px 18px;background:#10b981;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;" %>
</p>

<p style="font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#9ca3af;line-height:1.5;">
  If you didn't sign up for Ike, you can ignore this email — the account stays inactive until it's confirmed.
</p>

<p style="font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#9ca3af;line-height:1.5;word-break:break-all;">
  Or copy and paste this URL:<br>
  <%= @confirm_url %>
</p>
